SLIDE 2: GROUP MEMBERS & HISTORY
----------------------------------------
Title: "The Original Five Members"
Content:
  • Lee Min-woo (이민우) - Leader, Main Vocalist (1998-2009, 2014-present)
  • Shin Hye-sung (신혜성) - Lead Vocalist
  • Kim Jong-min (김종민) - Main Dancer, Lead Rapper
  • Ahn Jung-hoon (안재훈) - Lead Dancer (1998-2005)
  & Eric Mun (문준호) - Lead Vocalist, Visual

Timeline:
  • 1998: Debut with "This Angel"
  • 2001-2016: Military enlistment period
  • 2016-present: Active group activities continue

