SLIDE 4: LEGACY & ACHIEVEMENTS
----------------------------------------
Title: "Why Shinhwa is Legendary"
Key Achievements:
  ✅ Longest-running K-Pop group (25+ years)
  ✅ Over 15 studio albums
  ✅ Multiple music show wins
  ✅sold-out concert tours across Asia
  ✅ Cultivated loyal fandom "Shinera" (신나라)

Impact on K-Pop Industry:
  • Pioneered group longevity in idol industry
  • Influenced subsequent generations of artists
  • Maintained unity through military service
  • Continued success into 4th generation era

